"title": "2212: Jesus Christ, head of the church",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "2212",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Jesus Christ rules and governs his people and directs them towards the fulfilment of God's purposes. All power and authority within the church derive from Jesus Christ as the head.</p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ rules the universe in the interest of the church</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:22-Eph1:23\">EPH 1:22–1:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:10\">EPH 1:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:18\">COL 1:18</a></p>\n<h2>All power and authority within the church derive from Jesus Christ as the head</h2>\n<h3>Jesus Christ is recognised as head of the church</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:15\">EPH 4:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:23\">EPH 5:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:19\">COL 2:19</a></p>\n<h3>Within the church Jesus Christ alone rules with authority</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:8-Matt23:10\">MAT 23:8–23:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:13\">JHN 13:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:5\">2CO 4:5</a></p>\n<h3>The church owes obedience to its head</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:15\">JHN 14:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:21\">JHN 14:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:23\">JHN 14:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:24\">EPH 5:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:24\">1JN 3:24</a></p>\n<h3>All human authority in the church derives from its head</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:11\">EPH 4:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal1:1\">GAL 1:1</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ is the cornerstone and builder of the church</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:20-Eph2:22\">EPH 2:20–2:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:18\">MAT 16:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:11\">ACT 4:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps118:22\">PSA 118:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:4-1Pet2:6\">1PE 2:4–2:6</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's role as head of the church</h2>\n<h3>He loves the church</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:25\">EPH 5:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:11\">JHN 10:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:2\">EPH 5:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:23\">EPH 5:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:16\">1JN 3:16</a></p>\n<h3>He cares for the church</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev7:17\">REV 7:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:14-John10:15\">JHN 10:14–10:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:27-John10:28\">JHN 10:27–10:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:12\">JHN 17:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:29-Eph5:30\">EPH 5:29–5:30</a></p>\n<h3>He provides for the growth of the church</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:19\">COL 2:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:15-Eph4:16\">EPH 4:15–4:16</a></p>\n<h3>He prays for the church</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:20-John17:26\">JHN 17:20–17:26</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:34\">ROM 8:34</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb7:25\">HEB 7:25</a></p>\n<h3>He judges the church</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:23\">REV 2:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:10-Rom14:12\">ROM 14:10–14:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:10\">2CO 5:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:8\">EPH 6:8</a></p>\n<h3>He will present the church blameless before God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:27\">EPH 5:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:14\">2CO 4:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:22\">COL 1:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:24\">JUD 1:24</a></p>",
